works.description: If you want to bring nature indoors with one-of-a-kind furniture units, you might love to consider the Mangrove Chair from Veraseri Designs. Designed by Adam Krehbiel, the bold yet beautiful Mangrove Chair is the first in a series of unique sculptural works where purposed niche design is demanded as high as function and stand-alone balance. The unusual chair was created as a reaction to our planet’s dying Mangrove ecosystems.
